{"word":"G2229 - ἦ - ē - ay - Surely","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἦ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ē</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ay</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Surely</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"நிச்சயமாக - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"assuredly, most certainly, full surely"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>An adverb of <i>confirmation</i>; perhaps intensive of <a href=\"#/G2228 - ἤ - ḗ - ay/2228\">G2228</a>; used only (in the N. T.) before <a href=\"#/G3303 - μέν - mén - men/3303\">G3303</a>; <i>assuredly:</i> - surely.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}